[Name] LibV4L
[Summary] Userspace library for V4L
[Description] Userspace library which can be used to (very) easily add support for all kind of pixelformats to v4l2 applications. libv4l2 will then do conversion of any known (webcam) pixelformats to bgr24 or yuv420.
[License] LGPL 2.1+
[Homepage] http://hansdegoede.livejournal.com/3636.html
